WEBVTT

00:00:00.869 --> 00:00:02.620
Four years ago,

00:00:02.620 --> 00:00:04.422
a security researcher,

00:00:04.422 --> 00:00:08.671
or, as most people would call it, a hacker,

00:00:08.671 --> 00:00:10.838
found a way to literally

00:00:10.838 --> 00:00:14.041
make ATMs throw money at him.

00:00:14.041 --> 00:00:17.382
His name was Barnaby Jack,

00:00:17.382 --> 00:00:21.041
and this technique was later called "jackpotting"

00:00:21.041 --> 00:00:22.950
in his honor.

00:00:22.950 --> 00:00:24.799
I'm here today because I think

00:00:24.799 --> 00:00:27.850
we actually need hackers.

00:00:27.850 --> 00:00:29.712
Barnaby Jack

00:00:29.712 --> 00:00:31.199
could have easily turned